| **Phase 1: Discovery** | **Phase 2: Cell Formation** | **Phase 3: Operations** |
|:----------------------:|:---------------------------:|:-----------------------:|
| **O(√n)** | **O(k²)** | **O(n log n)** |
| Geographic Beacons | Leader Election | Hierarchical Routing |
| (Geohash-based) | Capability Aggregation | State Aggregation |
| Constrained Search | Role Assignment | Command Propagation |

