## Deployment Scenarios: Tactical vs Garrison

::: columns
:::: column

### Tactical Edge (Offline)

**Environment:**

- No internet connectivity
- GPS-denied
- Contested RF spectrum

**Security Adaptations:**

- Pre-provisioned certificates
- Local CRLs (offline revocation)
- Short-lived session tokens
- Local authorization decisions

**Trade-off:** Security vs availability

::::
:::: column

### Garrison (Connected)

**Environment:**

- Reliable internet
- GPS available
- Uncontested networks

**Security Enhancements:**

- Online Certificate Status Protocol (OCSP)
- CAC/PIV integration
- Centralized audit log aggregation
- Real-time threat intelligence

**Trade-off:** Maximum security

::::
:::

**Adaptive Policy:** System detects environment and adjusts security posture

