## Appendix C: Architecture Diagrams

**HIVE Protocol Stack:**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Application Layer                      │
│  (Cell Formation, Capability Comp)      │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Coordination Layer                     │
│  (Hierarchical Routing, Aggregation)    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Sync Layer (Automerge CRDT)            │
│  (Conflict Resolution, State Merge)     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Transport Layer (Iroh QUIC)            │
│  (Multi-path, Stream Multiplexing)      │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Network Layer                          │
│  (Ethernet, Starlink, MANET, 5G)        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Data Flow (Bottom-Up):**

1. Network interfaces receive packets
2. Iroh QUIC demultiplexes streams
3. Automerge merges CRDT state
4. Coordination layer aggregates by hierarchy
5. Application consumes cell/capability state

